descript.abstract:
Natural Earth A public domain dataset available at 1:10m, 1:50m, and 1:110m scales. Featuring tightly integrated vector and raster data.
Rivers (1:10m) feature class, ne_10m_rivers_lake_centerlines Railroads (1:10m) feature class, ne_10m_railroads Roads (1:10m), feature class, ne_10m_roads Populated Places (1:10m) feature class, ne_10m_populated_places
